By: FE Online | Updated: March 19, 2017 3:19 PM In a move that surprised many, ex-Chief Minister of Uttar Pradesh Akhilesh Yadav has arrived at Smriti Upwan to attend the swearing-in ceremony of the newly elected CM of the state Yogi Adityanath. (Source: ANI) 
In a move that surprised many, ex-Chief Minister of Uttar Pradesh Akhilesh Yadav has arrived at Smriti Upwan to attend the swearing-in ceremony of the newly elected CM of the state Yogi Adityanath. As the firebrand BJP leader is all set to take oath as the 32nd chief minister of UP, the ceremony is being embraced by some prominent leaders from various opposition parties.
